## Before running ohmyzsh installation setup, make sure zsh, polkit and git packages are installed

## Packages to remove

foot
dmenu
vim

## MAKE SURE TO RUN "paru -c" AFTER REMOVING PACKAGES TO CLEAN UP LEFTOVER DEPENDENCIES

